              span Lorem ipsum dolor, sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Sequi adipisci qui et necessitatibus culpa eligendi sit odit, obcaecati quia quo? Recusandae ipsum qui mollitia totam maxime possimus quam repellat earum!
      +section()
        +ui-h4('Lazy load test')
        br
        img.lazyload(src='../../images/swim.jpg' data-src='../../images/fancy_img1.png' alt='')
      +section()
        +ui-h4('Lazy load test')
        br
        img.lazyload(src='../../images/swim.jpg' data-src='../../images/fancy_img2.png' alt='')
